//Program to check whether the no is +ve or-ve

int main()
{
    float a;
    printf("\n enter a number:");
    scanf("%f",&a);
    if(a<0)
        printf("\n number is negative");
    else
        printf("\n number is positive");
}


Output:
enter a number:
56

 number is positive

AND
enter a number:
-78

 number is negative

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/check-whether-number-is-positive-or.html
